enum mycrate::Color

pub enum Color

Represents a color.

Variants:
  Blue(u8)                                                    The color blue with intensity.
  Green                                                       The color green.
  Red                                                         The color red.

Methods:
  pub fn name(&self) -> &str                                  Returns the color name.
